title: Niobia Bryant-Never Keeping Secrets
description:
Four friends are reunited, but the occasion is bittersweet--and filled with secrets and scandal. . ..

Monica, a CEO with celebrity clients, loves her life. But when her man loses his high-powered corporate job and pressures her to start a family, Monica finds herself involved with a client who wants to mix business with pleasure--or else. . .Successful author Keesha is blowing through her money--and cheating on her fiancÃƒÂ©. When her new friend, Jeremiah, discovers her deception, Keesha stands to lose everything. . .

Danielle has fame and fortune as a TV co-host. Her relationships are strictly for pleasure--until she reconnects with the only man she ever loved. But Danielle wasn't looking for love. . .or for the secrets from her past being used to torment her. . .

A full-time mom and preacher's wife, Latoya is feeling the strain of living under the eye of the church. Her only relief comes from the pills no one knows she's popping. At least she thinks no one knows. . .
